item.title: Prayer bpn4920 in Vanuatu
item.description: Ol glori i go long Yu, O God blong mi. I tru se man mo woman ia i tufala wokman blong Yu. Tufala i bin kam wan ples anda long sado blong sori blong Yu. Mo tufala i save joen tugeta from we Yu Yu agri mo Yu Yu kaen tu mas. O God! Helpem tufala long tisfala wol blong Yu, we Yu Yu Masta blong hem. Mekem se tufala i kasem evri gud samting, from we Yu Yu givim ol samting mo Yu Yu kaen.
